{"type":null,"faqId":44692,"title":"为什么手机经常突然屏幕卡住不动，屏幕四周出现黄框？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">原因是因为打开了放大手势功能，连续三次点击屏幕就会触发，触发后需要两个手指一起按上才能移动屏幕，或者再次三击屏幕才能还原。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">首次打开放大手势，三次点击屏幕会触发放大手势弹框，提示用户开启了放大手势的功能。用户可以选择“关闭手势”关闭放大手势功能，也可以点击“忽略”继续进行放大操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">这个是给老人或有视觉障碍人群使用的功能，请在“设置 &gt; 辅助功能 &gt; 放大手势“选择关闭</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"193","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409023000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":26,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"屏幕不动,字体很大,全屏,黄色的框","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}